item.title: Week 2
item.description: Good monday morning This week’s primary goal is to complete my native DNS resolver. It would be nice to get it done within 3 days. I like to have secondary projects/todos on the side so that if I hit a roadblock with the first one, there is something else to spend time on. There are couple of things in my mind I can watch Andy Pavlo’s lecture on database storage. maybe it can conjure some new project ideas (building a LSM tree?
